(639, 2, '2011-09-19 21:57:21', '2011-09-19 18:57:21', 'Norint vaizdƒÖ perkelti i≈° kompiuterio ƒØ TV jums prireiks:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ne≈°iojamo kompiuterio</li>\r\n	<li>Skaitmeninio televizoriaus</li>\r\n	<li>Vieno i≈° video kabeli≈≥:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>S-Video</li>\r\n	<li>VGA 15-pin</li>\r\n	<li>DVI</li>\r\n	<li>DVI-to-HDMI</li>\r\n	<li>Mini-RCA audio kabelis</li>\r\n	<li>PC-TV konverteris</li>\r\n	<li>Mini-DVI ƒØ VGA arba mini-DVI ƒØ DVI adapteris, skirtas Apple kompiuteriams</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nPirmas ≈æingsnis: Prijungimas su S-Video kabeliu\r\n\r\nPrijunkite video kabeli, PC vartotojams patogiausia naudoti S-Video kabelƒØ, nes dauguma skaitmenini≈≥ televizori≈≥ turi S-Video priƒójimƒÖ.\r\nAntras ≈æingsnis: Prijungimas su VGA\r\n\r\nJei turite senesni HDTV, tuomet galite pabandyti VGA kabelƒØ, kuris padeda i≈°gauti geresnƒô rai≈°kos kokybƒô bei dirba tiek su Apple kompiuteriais, ties su PC. Norint prijungti su VGA kabeliu, pirma i≈°junkite savo TV ir ne≈°iojamƒÖ kompiuterƒØ. Suraskite trapecijos i≈°vaizdos ƒØƒójimƒÖ ir i≈°ƒójimƒÖ kompiuteryje bei televizoriuje, prijunkite kabelƒØ ir vƒól ƒØjunkite abu prietaisus.\r\n\r\nTreƒçias ≈æingsnis: Prijungimas su DVI kabeliu\r\n\r\nDVI jungties rai≈°kos kokybƒó yra laipteliu auk≈°ƒçiau nei VGA, taƒçiau tik naujesni kompiuteriai ir HDTV turi DVI jungtis. Sujungimas vykdoma taip pat kaip ir VGI jungties.\r\n\r\nKetvirtas ≈æingnis: Prijungimas su HDMI kabeliu\r\n\r\nJei jusu HDTV neturi DVI jungties, tuomet naudokite kabelƒØ, kurio vienam gale HDMI, o kitam DVI jungtis.\r\n\r\nPenktas ≈æingsnis: Audio prijungimas\r\n\r\nHook up the audio. After you''ve connected your laptop to the TV via video cable, connect the mini-to-RCA cable from your computer''s headphone jack to your TV.\r\n\r\nStep 6: Use a wireless converter\r\n\r\nA final PC option is to go wireless, using a converter box and the software that comes with it. Using a VGA cable, plug the box into your TV and install the software onto your computer. The box will then convert your computer''s VGA signal to the TV, and transfer both video and audio.\r\n\r\nStep 7: Adjust display settings\r\n\r\nIf you have a PC, go to the Control Panel and adjust the display settings to accompany double display on both your monitor and TV set. Mac laptops should automatically adjust for double display. If yours doesn''t, go to System Preferences, click on Display, and then Detect Displays.\r\n\r\nStep 8: Find your laptop\r\n\r\nClick your TV''s video source -- usually a button called "input" or "TV/Video" on your remote -- until your laptop comes up. You''re set!\r\n\r\nThanks for watching How To Connect Your Laptop To Your Television! If you enjoyed this video subscribe to the Howcast YouTube channel!', 'I≈° ne≈°iojamo ƒØ TV', '<iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/0GzaKfCtzb0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '346-revision-8', '', '', '2011-09-19 21:57:21', '2011-09-19 18:57:21', '', 346, 'http://re-startas.lt/?p=639', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
